{"tid":1908753,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"機票跳樓價 深圳飛成都僅5元","createTime":"2020-03-03T13:22:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T06:28:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"98a614247f2bb3feadc56499741dea3f003a81dc","tid":1908753,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T13:22:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200303/PACGAOCRWAKRAI4W4XO53FQ4SM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200303%2FPACGAOCRWAKRAI4W4XO53FQ4SM%2F&d=HqwfJ7ndl2RLmQbQQ2LVposqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=32d0be28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200303%2FPACGAOCRWAKRAI4W4XO53FQ4SM%2F&h=66c9170e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200303/PACGAOCRWAKRAI4W4XO53FQ4SM/</a><br />\n<br />\n機票跳樓價 深圳飛成都僅5元<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200303/large/1583165836_7968.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200303%2Flarge%2F1583165836_7968.gif&h=bbac6e6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5元人民幣（下同，約5.6元港幣）可以買甚麼？一杯咖啡都不夠！但在武漢肺炎疫情籠罩下，竟可買到一張深圳飛成都的機票（未含稅油）。內地機票湧現「跳樓價」，數十或百多元人民幣的機票俯拾皆是，有網民笑稱「坐飛機比巴士還便宜」。專家估計內地民航業上月收入損失近370億（約411億港幣）。在中共大力催谷下內地復工復產，至2月底逾九成酒店恢復營業。<br />\n<br />\n疫情重挫內地航空業，損失嚴重的航空公司忍痛自救，推出超低折扣價惠。上海飛重慶最低只需49元、折扣低至0.3折；廣州飛中國西部多個城市低見一折機票，2月29日飛成都最平120元。有網民貼出深圳飛成都機票，票價才5元（不含稅，圖），表示「以前還是飛的，現在飛公交」。專家估算，內地民航上月收入損失370億，3月預計收入損失約350億（約388億港元）。疫情若延到四、五月，行業損失可能上千億。<br />\n<br />\n硬推復工 九成酒店重開<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：單日顧客11,528人創紀錄<br />\n<br />\n隨着中共當局下令復產救經濟，許多停業酒店開始復業。據旅遊平台數據，2月底逾九成酒店恢復營業，其中廣州、深圳酒店營業數回復至1月初水平，上海、成都等熱門城市更有超過95%恢復營業。上周酒店入住人數則較前一周增83%。有預訂平台為讓入住者安心推「疫情雷達」，只要打開手機地圖，酒店周邊是否有疫症病例一目了然。<br />\n<br />\n中新社/21世紀經濟網"},{"pid":"b62899f604dd5ea64837b66d2f076795b2e25e25","tid":1908753,"uid":92476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T13:24:37.000Z","msg":"想飛去播毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"654186c384efccd1008a5f541104c410b441e9cf","tid":1908753,"uid":4243,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T13:25:49.000Z","msg":"去AIA玩轉跳樓機止唔止5蚊？"},{"pid":"008ebca2d17aaad272f52e344095187f27b1ca0a","tid":1908753,"uid":189638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T13:39:47.000Z","msg":"好多支那人連門口都出唔到，出到自己社區已經叫勁<br />\n仲可以周圍走嘅唔知仲剩幾多人"},{"pid":"f970d86a9b803c86ca5b141deb876cab0be66691","tid":1908753,"uid":252506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T13:43:10.000Z","msg":"唔關疫情事,係回程機,好耐之前由廣州去海南都係7蚊人仔"},{"pid":"29c3329615ea423b9965ebe9fefdebc496c31e9c","tid":1908753,"uid":339272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T13:50:26.000Z","msg":"相信黨 冇事 yeah"},{"pid":"a356079e4bf2b31dff4f59f73fcfec44478a6f63","tid":1908753,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:05:11.000Z","msg":"我屌sa你哋班YellowNazi老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1907722\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1907722</a>"},{"pid":"64f92f4b8f2520efc920079bb0a6d2a968fa32b0","tid":1908753,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T14:07:51.000Z","msg":"倒貼好過啦"},{"pid":"2606a3fccd28842eb79140b55de5851a5db4abf4","tid":1908753,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T06:28:33.000Z","msg":"唔會再去支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}